data.description: Turn-key and fully updated under $160k! Move right into this updated 2 bed 1 bath in a quiet neighborhood. The fenced backyard is great for privacy and detached 1 stall garage has room for storage. New plumbing March '22, Furnace & Central A/C March '22, Attic Insulation April '22, and Roof in 2021. All you need to do is move in. Call today for your private showing!
